  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\nTo keep things simple, we decided to drop the Community Description from inside the message we send when doing Share Community (Add member on the UI).\r\n\r\nInstead, we will just share the community link in the message.\r\n\r\nIt will then be handled as usual.\r\n1. Get the data from the DB if it is there or show a loading state\r\n2. Sub to topics\r\n3. Fetch from store nodes\r\n4. Update with any new description received\r\n\r\nThis above should all already be present in the app, so just the backend part is needed to be changed.\r\n\r\n#### Notes\r\n\r\n- Make sure mobile supports the links so we don,t break anything for them\r\n- Don,' use the data in the received URL, just the ID and shard info to fetch from store nodes\r\n",
